GIVEAWAY! 🎄🎅 CLOSED

To celebrate the holiday season, I’m giving away one (1) golden cod pendant necklace OR (1) cuff bracelet (your choice!). My mission with @thegoldencod was to create a collection where you felt like you had a little piece of New England with you wherever you go.

To enter:

🎄 follow me @robbinmangano + like this post
🎄 follow @thegoldencod 
🎄 tag a friend in the comments to tell them about the giveaway too! 

Giveaway ends on Sunday, December 4 at 6pm EST. Winner will be randomly selected - must reside in the U.S.

Miami 🌴 plus, Jack on the baby cam 😂 (last pic)

Ferry commutes home to @hinghamshipyard 💙There’s nothing better than when your commute home from Boston happens to turn into dinner and a boat cruise. #sponsored

The waterfront destination has a ton of great retail, dining, and wellness options, which makes it the perfect place to plan a weeknight date with my sister and adorable niece, while also grabbing a few grocery staples before heading home. 

We started at @thebethhingham, then strolled over to @thefreshmarket for some wine and cheese ahead of my book club party. 

For my Boston + South Shore friends, I’m excited to share that I’m partnering with @hinghamshipyard to give away a $50 gift card to experience their restaurants and retailers this holiday season. To enter to win, comment below your fave place to spend time at in the Hingham Shipyard (restaurant, shop, workout studio, anything!), and make sure you’re following @hinghamshipyard on IG. I’ll pick one (1) winner on November 10, 2023.
Finally booked fam photos after 5 years of forgetting to order holiday cards 🤪 // 📷 @morganwynnephotography
Lots of babies, cousins, turkeys, trots, siblings, pies, & grandparents.
… and to all a good night 🎄
